WEBVTT

00:07:29.625 --> 00:07:31.846
LB: Well, the way forward
is still the same.

00:07:31.870 --> 00:07:33.125
Rapid detection,

00:07:33.149 --> 00:07:34.768
rapid response.

00:07:34.792 --> 00:07:36.260
Finding every case,

00:07:36.284 --> 00:07:39.434
and then figuring out all the contacts.

00:07:39.458 --> 00:07:41.840
We've got great new technology
for contact tracing,

00:07:41.864 --> 00:07:45.315
we've got amazing scientists
working at the speed of light

00:07:45.339 --> 00:07:48.974
to give us test kits
and antivirals and vaccines.

00:07:48.998 --> 00:07:51.879
We need to slow down,

00:07:51.903 --> 00:07:54.966
the Buddhists say slow down time

00:07:54.990 --> 00:07:58.337
so that you can put your heart,
your soul, into that space.

00:07:58.361 --> 00:08:01.273
We need to slow down
the speed of this virus,